    <p><strong>Business Summary</strong><br />
  TEC Recycling is an air conditioning appliance recycler. We specialize in the recycling of all air conditioning&nbsp;appliances including PTACs and PTHPs (Package Terminal Air Conditioners and Package Terminal Heat Pumps). Our goal is to help the environment through the proper recycling of these units and the refrigerant found within. </p>
